  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1027">
<l>amarakattu vaṉkaṇṇar pōlat tamarakattu</l>
<l>māṟṟuvār mēṟṟē poṟai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like heroes in the battle-field, the burden (of protection etc.) is borne by those who are the most efficient in a family.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
